title: QUESTIONS - Good Omens
author: Koji Dub
comment: I've never seen this take on "they knew each other before the fall" it's beautiful

THE FRENCH MAKES ITS ALL THE MORE LOVELY THIS COMIC IS ONE OF MY FAVORITES MERCI 
(apologize for my bad attempt of French)
The 4 dislikes are from Gabriel, belzebub, hastur and Michael

I wasn’t ready for how heartbreaking this would be. The voice actors did an amazing job and the French really brought out the emotion in my opinion. So all I can do is applaud you for how genius this is.
They voices are so good I even though they were from a comic then everything fit perfectly and I got so confused... But no... It's just this amazing talent and creativity
description:
Heya tout le monde !
Enfin! Voilà une vidéo que je désirais sortir depuis très longtemps! Encore sur Good Omens, il s'agit d'un prequel à la série.
Cela aura nécessité beaucoup de doubleurs et fut un gros travail de montage, mais le contenu est disponible!!!

Merci beaucoup à l’artiste Blooming Cyre pour sa patience et son autorisation pour le doublage de son œuvre !
